FireResist 5

Contract Killer (Su)
1/day, free action
Declare a creature you have marked for death.
+2/+2 vs that creature for the day.
The target may be any specific creature known of, even if you've not seen the target before.

Locate Creature (Sp)
At Will, Full-Round action
Range: 400 ft + 40 ft/level
You slowly turn and sense when you are facing in the direction of the creature you have marked for death, provided it is within range.
You also know in which direction the creature is moving, if any.
Running water blocks the spell. It cannot detect objects. It can be fooled by mislead, nondetection, and polymorph spells.


